================================================================================
REFERENCE IMPLEMENTATIONS (no code copied)
================================================================================

kitty
License: GPL-3.0
https://github.com/kovidgoyal/kitty

The font rendering pipeline (src/font.rs, src/text.wgsl) was independently
implemented using kitty's source as a reference for technique and correctness.
No kitty source code was copied. Specifically, kitty's approach to FreeType
hinting flag selection, glyph atlas construction, monospace cell grid
computation, and sRGB-aware contrast adjustment informed our implementation.
